5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

frame-manager-palette

Generic function

Summary

Returns the palette used by the specified frame manager.

Signature

frame-manager-palette framem => palette

Arguments

framem
An instance of type <frame-manager>.

Values

palette
An instance of type <palette>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the palette used by framem.

See also

frame-manager-palette-setter, page 281

Functional Developer Library Reference: DUIM - 3 Dec 1998
